"President Xi Jinping Sends Congratulations Letter to the 2021 Greater Bay Area Scientific Forum-Xinhua News"
"President Xi Jinping sent a congratulations letter to the 2021 Greater Bay Area Scientific Forum on December 11th, Beijing.”
"President Xi Jinping pointed out that the world is currently experiencing a hundred-year-old unprecedented major change, the global technological innovation has entered an intensive and active period, and the new round of technological revolution and industrial transformation has had a profound impact on the global economic structure.”
"The Greater Bay Area of Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macao should focus on the strategy of building an international center for scientific and technological innovation, strive to build a global high ground for technological innovation, and promote the development of emerging industries.”
"China is willing to work closely with scientists from all over the world and international science and technology organizations to closely cooperate in international scientific and technological exchange, strengthen research on major scientific issues, promote the resolution of common scientific and technological problems, deepen cooperation on key scientific projects, and jointly promote the development of the world's scientific cause and better benefit humanity."
"The 2021 Greater Bay Area Scientific Forum opened on the same day in Guangzhou, Guangdong Province with the theme of "Exploring the Future, Sharing Science", sponsored by the People's Government of Guangdong Province."